## CHANGELOG
------------------------------------------------------------------------
## Name: Archey
## Desc: A command line system information tool written in Python.
------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------
## 0.2.8
- Reworked the File system function.
- Major cleanup in the color scheme.
- Added color to disk and ram outputs similar to screenfo.
------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------
## 0.2.7
- Added support for Linux Mint
------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------
## 0.2.6
- Added support for Fedora
- Added support for CrunchBang
------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------
## 0.2.5
- Added support for Debian
------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------
## 0.2.4
- Removed coloring, Archey will only output arch logo in blue
- Added dynamic support for arch linux detection
- Added support for Ubuntu
------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------
## 0.2.3
- Added Terminal detection
- Removed support for battery
------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------
## 0.2.2
- Updated WM and DE functions; archey will now only report WM/DE if 
present
- Added Shell Detection
------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------
## 0.2.1
- Automatic filesystem detection (it will only display the first 7 
mounts)
- Currently supports: ext2 ext3 ext4 reiserfs jfs ntfs fat32 btrfs 
- Some cleanup
------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------
## 0.2.0
- Support for ratpoison
- Switched back to scrot for screenshot function
- Scrot is now a required dependency as opposed to being optional in 
previous versions
------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------
## 0.1.11
- Major cleanup
------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------
## 0.1.10
- Support for ScrotWM
------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------
## 0.1.6
- xmonad bug fixed
- Cleanup in CPU function
------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------
## 0.1.5
- Support for PekWM
- Support for Musca WM
- CPU Model Reporting
- RAM Usage Reporting
------------------------------------------------------------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------
## 0.1.0 
- First Release
------------------------------------------------------------------------
